drop table "SYS_Role" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "SYS_Role" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "SYS_Role"
(
"RoleID" NUMBER(10) not null,
"REMRoleId" VARCHAR2(50),
"WFCode" VARCHAR2(50),
"RoleCode" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"RoleName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"isAdmin" INTEGER not null,
"SourceFrom" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_SYS_ROLE primary key ("RoleID")
);

comment on table "SYS_Role" is
'角色';

comment on column "SYS_Role"."isAdmin" is
'1:Admin
2:非Admin';

comment on column "SYS_Role"."SourceFrom" is
'1: 来自老REM系统
0: 来自可视化系统';

comment on column "SYS_Role"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';
